### List active customers
GET http://localhost:8080/api/customers?status=ACTIVE

### Search customer across active / inactive by calling each status list
GET http://localhost:8080/api/customers?status=ACTIVE&search=arya

### List inactive customers
GET http://localhost:8080/api/customers?status=INACTIVE&search=arya

### List categories
GET http://localhost:8080/api/categories

### Add category
POST http://localhost:8080/api/categories
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Desserts"
}

### List in-stock items
GET http://localhost:8080/api/items?inStock=true

### Add item
POST http://localhost:8080/api/items
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Brownie Shake",
  "price": 159.00,
  "inStock": true,
  "categoryId": 2
}

### Add customer
POST http://localhost:8080/api/customers
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Nova Crunch",
  "orderLines": [
    { "itemId": 1, "quantity": 1 },
    { "itemId": 3, "quantity": 1 }
  ]
}

### Update customer name
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/customers/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Arya Blaze Prime"
}

### Add order line
POST http://localhost:8080/api/customers/1/order-lines
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "itemId": 2,
  "quantity": 1
}

### Mark payment successful and move to inactive
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/customers/1/status
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "INACTIVE"
}

### Move inactive user back to active
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/customers/1/status
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "ACTIVE"
}
